N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 175.9 - Delays caused by unforeseen cause

State Regulations

Delays caused by accident, act of God or other unforeseen
cause are extraordinary occurrences which could not be foreseen or prevented. Such delays do not include routine performance of services as are incidental to
employment. Notes
